1. d4{ Welcome to the first chapter on the Catalan! This is one of the most important ones in the whole course. Many strong players employ this opening and theory is constantly evolving.    It is one of the most solid openings and White hopes for small edges and tries to build up pressure slowly. There are many possible recipes against the Catalan, but I do hope that you will enjoy my recommendation! }
1. d5
2. c4
2. e6
