5. c5{ Here we go with ... c5  and ... Nc6 , hitting in the center quickly. }
6. O-O
6. Nc6
7. Qa4{ One of the main lines. White is intending to play  Ne5  next move. }
7. Bd7{ Unpinning the knight. }
8. Qxc4
8. b5
