13. Bd2
13. Bxd2
14. Rxd2
14. Ke7{ A very strong move. The king is safe, and Black can continue with ... Rad8  and ... Bc6 . }
15. Nc5( 15.Nd6 Rad8! 16.Nxb7 Nxb7 17.Bxb7 Ba4! { , when Black dominates the d-file and has the initiative. } )
15. Rad8
16. Bxb7( 16.Nxb7 { transposes to the   }15.Nd6 { line. } )
16. Bc6
