13. cxd4{ White manages to fix the pawn structure. }
13. Nd5{ The best move, closing in the  g2 -bishop and preparing ... Nc3  as well as ... b6  and ... Bb7 . Also, Black can play ... f5 , fighting against the  e4  push. There are many options for White now. }
14. Bd2
