16. Nc6
16. Bf6{ White has many options, but I think Black equalizes. }
17. Rac1( 17.Bb4 Re8 18.Rac1 Bb7 19.Be1 Rec8 { was played in ½-½ Froewis-Hess, Germany 2022, and Black's position is okay. } )
