10. cxd4
11. exd4( { After }11.Nxd4 Nxc3 12.bxc3 Nd7 { , Black has a clear advantage, as White's structure is very bad. } )
11. Nc6
12. O-O
12. Rc8
13. Re1
13. Ncb4{ Black threatens to win the bishop pair and the  a2 -pawn is hanging; this is a bad version of the isolated pawn for White. }
