6. b6( { The first important moment. Black can play }6...c5 { or }6...Nbd7 { , which are perfectly fine moves. }6...b6 { is a more quiet move. Here, }{ White has many options, including taking on  d5 , developing the bishop, or other moves like }{   }7.Qc2 { , }7.Rc1 { , }7.a3 { , etc. } )
