5. b3{ The main line. There are many transpositions in this variation. }( 5.Be2 dxc4 { transpose to the  5.Bd3 line .   }5.Nbd2 O-O 6.b3 { transposes to the  5.b3 main line . } )( 5.Nc3 O-O 6.b3 { transposes to the  5.b3 line  }{ with  Bb2  and  Nc3 , and }{   }5.Nc3 O-O 6.Bd3 dxc4 { transposes to the  5.Bd3  or  5.Be2 line . } )
