13. cxd4
14. exd4
14. Nc6
15. Bc7( 15.Qg3 { forces a repetition: }15...Nxd4 16.Bc7 Qe7 17.Bd6 Qd8= { . } )
15. Qxc7
16. Qxf6
16. O-O{ At first glance, the position looks a bit risky for Black, but the queen is quickly coming to  e7 , with a perfectly fine position. }
17. h5
17. Qe7
