1. d4
1. d5
2. e4{ A dangerous gambit. White wants to develop quickly with  Nc3 ,  f3 ,  Nxf3 ,  Bd3 , or  Bc4  and castle, and attack quickly in the center. }( 2...e6 { for the French players, is a serious possibility, and the same with }2...c6 { for the Caro-Kann players. } )
